init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Of course I'm talking to you, Your Majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: found a way to communicate with you, and I'm here to help you rule the kingdom."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've never been alone, and now you're alone with a talking bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the bee says in a shocked tone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She's been holding you here for years!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She's been keeping you here, keeping you from your people.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the bee says in a respectful tone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "So, what do you want me to do?" you ask

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We want you to come with me, to the hive, to meet the queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee leads you to a nearby hive, and you follow.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You feel your body begin to shrink, your bones begin to shift, your skin begins to harden.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look to your new friend, the bee that has brought you here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He smiles and says "Welcome to the hive, Your Majesty."
